    <div class="policy-container">
        <h1>Shipping Policy</h1>
        <h2>How does Mzuri Express deliver?</h2>
        <p>For deliveries around Kampala, Wakiso and Entebbe districts, we use our local delivery agents. Our delivery means include a motorcycle, tricycle, or a truck. For deliveries outside the mentioned areas, we process orders through a delivery courier that transports your item to your location.</p>

        <h2>How much is the delivery?</h2>
        <p>Delivery cost varies depending on the area, size of the product, and weight of the product. You will be contacted by a delivery party with a detailed pricing and you can negotiate about it. We do not have fixed delivery costs.</p>
        <div class="note">
            <strong>NOTE:</strong> We share only your contact information specifically your name and phone number with the party to deliver your item. Therefore, you should expect a delivery personnel or a courier service to contact you as soon as your order is ready for delivery.
        </div>
        <div class="note">
            <strong>NOTE:</strong><p>All prices of the products on this website do not include delivery fees</p>
        </div>
        <h2>How long does my order take to arrive?</h2>
        <p>Areas within Kampala, Wakiso and Entebbe. It takes a maximum of 3 hours to get your ordered item delivered to you.</p>
        <p>At our physical location (Aponye Mall Opposite Old Taxi Park, Shop number MA22). Buying an item takes less than 5 minutes.</p>

        <h2>Does Mzuri Express ship internationally?</h2>
        <p>No, we do not ship internationally. We deliver only within Uganda. You can order an item from anywhere in the world but the delivery location should be within Uganda.</p>

        <h2>Are there delivery restrictions?</h2>
        <p>No, there are no delivery restrictions currently.</p>

        <h2>How can I track my order?</h2>
        <p>Get in touch with us. We assign a sales personnel to each and every client that orders. When you want to track your item, you can call them directly or send a WhatsApp message.</p>

        <h2>What should I do if my order hasnâ€™t arrived?</h2>
        <p>In summary, call or message us. In case of delay, we shall communicate with you with a detailed reason for the delay. However, you can come to our physical location if you are around Kampala.</p>

        <h2>Do you offer free shipping? If so, what are the conditions?</h2>
        <p>We don't offer free shipping.</p>

        <h2>What are your order processing times?</h2>
        <p>Order processing time is about 30 minutes on working days from 9am to 6pm. On weekends, it is 2 hours.</p>

        <h2>Do you ship to PO Boxes or APO/FPO addresses?</h2>
        <p>No, we do not ship to PO Boxes or APO/FPO addresses.</p>

        <h2>Can I change my shipping address after placing an order?</h2>
        <p>Yes you can only if you inform us through a phone call or messaging.</p>

        <h2>What carriers do you use for shipping?</h2>
        <p>For deliveries around Kampala, Wakiso and Entebbe districts, we use our local delivery agents. Our delivery means include a motorcycle, tricycle, or a truck. For deliveries outside the mentioned areas, we process orders through a delivery courier that transports your item to your location.</p>

        <h2>Do you offer local pickup options?</h2>
        <p>Yes we do, our physical pick up location is at Aponye Mall Opposite Old Taxi Park Shop Number MA22.</p>

        <h1>Return Policy</h1>
        <h2>How long do I have to return an item?</h2>
        <p>You have up to 7 days to return an item that meets requirements of return.</p>

        <h2>What items are eligible for return?</h2>
        <p>All items are eligible for return. The item should not be in damaged, unusable state, or have been used many times.</p>

        <h2>Are there any items that cannot be returned?</h2>
        <p>No, all items can be returned. The item should not be in damaged, unusable state, or have been used many times. Any item that has been repaired or unscrewed by other mechanics cannot be returned.</p>

        <h2>How do I initiate a return?</h2>
        <p>Communicate with us through a phone call or message.</p>

        <h2>Do you offer exchanges?</h2>
        <p>No, we don't offer exchanges.</p>

        <h2>Will I be charged for return shipping?</h2>
        <p>All return shipping costs are on you.</p>

        <h2>How will I receive my refund?</h2>
        <p>You will be refunded through cash when at our physical store and mobile money or bank transfer when not at the physical store.</p>

        <h2>How long does it take to process a return?</h2>
        <p>Processing a return can take up to 14 working days.</p>

        <h2>What should I do if I receive a damaged or defective item?</h2>
        <p>It is not possible. We test your item before it is delivered. However, when damaged on delivery, all costs are put on the delivering party. We exchange the damaged item for another similar one. We handle all damage on delivery issues. A customer is not involved in them.</p>

        <h2>Do you offer store credit for returns?</h2>
        <p>No, we do not offer store credit for returns.</p>

        <h2>What happens if I return an item after the return period?</h2>
        <p>We do not accept items returned after the return period.</p>

        <h2>Can I return an item bought on sale or with a discount?</h2>
        <p>Yes, you can return an item bought on sale or with a discount.</p>

        <h2>What is your policy on returning customized or personalized items?</h2>
        <p>Our policy on returning customized or personalized items is the same as our standard return policy.</p>

        <h2>Other points to note</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Make sure that you get a receipt after purchase. Do not accept a delivered item without a receipt or go with an item without a receipt.</li>
            <li>At Mzuri Express, we believe in customer interaction. Therefore, expect us to communicate with you through a phone call or messaging. Put it in mind that it is not possible to process an order without communicating with you.</li>
